channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: 4 dead, 6 injured after vehicle crashes into canal
item.description: Four people are dead and six others have been injured after a vehicle crashed into a canal in Palm Beach County, Florida, on Monday evening, authorities said.

item.title: ‘Our backs are against the wall’: The solar development that divided a rural community
Body recovered month after tourist drowns at Glacier National Park
item.description: Siddhant Vitthal Patil, 26, was one of two men who drowned over the July 4th weekend, park officials said.

item.title: Kamala Harris earns majority of Democratic roll call votes, achieving nomination
item.description: Vice President Kamala Harris has officially gotten the vast majority of delegate votes in the virtual roll call that nominates her as the Democratic presidential nominee.

item.title: Recreational marijuana sales are in Ohio. Here's where to buy it in Greater Cleveland
After Trump shooting, calls for violence and civil war spiked online
item.description: The day after the shooting at a Trump rally in Pennsylvania, the internet saw a huge spike in calls for violence, and in particular an increase in calls for a modern-day civil war, researchers say.

item.title: Fast-moving San Bernardino wildfire torches hillside community, forcing evacuations
item.description: Several homes burned Monday as a fast-moving wildfire torched a California hillside community, triggering evacuations while hundreds of firefighters tried to control the blaze

item.title: Diverging Diamond Interchange in Fort Myers: See what it looks like from our drone video
Whale makes surprise appearance during Olympic surfing competition
item.description: With all eyes on the ocean during the final day of the Paris Olympics surfing competition in Tahiti, a whale breached and gave spectators and photographers an amazing Olympics moment.

item.title: 911 operator calmly walks expectant mom through a surprise at-home delivery
item.description: A new mom in Nashville has 911 to thank for walking her through a surprise at-home birth

item.title: Warren Buffett Is Selling Apple Stock and Buying This Magnificent Megacap Stock Instead
Stocks rebound from rout as Fed faces calls to cut rates early
item.description: Most equities rallied Tuesday after the previous day's global rout fueled by U.S. recession fears that have led to calls for the Federal Reserve Board to cut interest rates before its next meeting.

item.title: Pelosi warns in her new book that political threats and violence 'must stop'
item.description: Not quite two years after the Jan. 6, 2021, attack at the Capitol, the threat of political violence would come for Nancy Pelosi's husband at their home

item.description: One step closer to gold, Team USA basketball moves on to the knockout round of the 2024 Summer Olympics Games.
